Memphis Depay is a target for Manchester United and Liverpool . 
  Bayern Munich have joined the race to sign the PSV Eindhoven winger . 
  Ronald de Boer has compared Depay to a young Cristiano Ronaldo . 
  The 21-year-old has played a key role in PSV winning the Eredivisie title . 
  Liverpool hope to convince Depay he would get more regular football with them . 
  Manchester United have also made a bid for the Holland international . 
 